    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="will-ai-replace-traditional-e-commerce-search"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>AI will not replace traditional search in the next 3 years, but it will sit alongside and partially absorb it. Practical Ecommerce reported in January 2026 that even when AI recommends a product, shoppers overwhelmingly prefer to leave the platform and visit the brand's website before purchasing. That means traditional search and brand sites continue to play a critical role. The shift is in the discovery and consideration stages, not in checkout — at least not yet, outside of the agentic commerce protocols.</p></div></div>
